e used to group commands, I'm guessing shows persistent flags in a `helm <subcommand> options`.\r\n\r\nI think there is no need to use a persistent flag for `helm status --revision` (a persistent flag is a flag that is inherited by sub-commands).  Note that the `--revision` flags of the different `helm get` commands are not persistent.\r\n\r\nOutput of `helm version`:\r\nversion.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.2+unreleased\", GitCommit:\"3779d959667095e03308a2e49480748f7911b228\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", GoVersion:\"go1.13.7\"}\r\n\r\n/cc @zgfh ","closed_by":{"login":"marckhouzam","id":414402,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQxNDQwMg==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/414402?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam","html_url":"https://github.com/marckhouzam","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marckhouzam/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/helm/helm/issues/8149/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/helm/helm/issues/8149/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}